   194	    /// @notice Checks if the given address is a contract
   195	    ///         Returns true for any account with runtime code (excluding EIP-7702 accounts).
   196	    ///         For EIP-7702 accounts, checks if code size is exactly 23 bytes (delegation format).
   197	    ///         Limitations:
   198	    ///         - Cannot distinguish between EOA and self-destructed contract
   199	    /// @param account The address to be checked
   200	    function isContract(address account) internal view returns (bool) {
   201	        uint256 size;
